1
00:00:00,358 --> 00:00:04,882
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,882 --> 00:00:10,386
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,386 --> 00:00:16,814
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,814 --> 00:00:21,294
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,294 --> 00:00:25,742
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,742 --> 00:00:30,653
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,653 --> 00:00:34,702
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,702 --> 00:00:39,237
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,237 --> 00:00:43,534
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,534 --> 00:00:48,299
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,299 --> 00:00:51,790
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,790 --> 00:00:55,470
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,116 --> 00:01:00,494
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,494 --> 00:01:03,182
=Episode 30=

15
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,900
This time, just be yourself.

16
00:01:07,366 --> 00:01:08,896
Jin Xi'er.

17
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:16,832
(Grandfather)

18
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:36,400
Chen, your father died
in a car accident when you were little,

19
00:01:36,700 --> 00:01:40,966
so I've put a lot of pressure
on you since then.

20
00:01:41,733 --> 00:01:45,233
I hoped you wouldn't
let your father down.

21
00:01:45,966 --> 00:01:48,500
That's why I made
many decisions for you.

22
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:56,333
I got you engaged to Miss Gu, hoping
you'd have an easy life after my death.

23
00:01:57,033 --> 00:01:59,533
But now you've grown up.

24
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:02,600
I support all your decisions.

25
00:02:12,736 --> 00:02:16,352
(Miss Jin)

26
00:02:31,170 --> 00:02:34,012
(Miss Jin)

27
00:02:37,019 --> 00:02:39,007
(Miss Jin)

28
00:02:59,552 --> 00:03:00,800
Miss Jin.

29
00:03:00,800 --> 00:03:03,933
- I...
- How dare you ignore four of my calls!

30
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:09,366
Meet me at Guodan Square right away.
I'm waiting for you.

31
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:13,933
It's late. I don't want to go out.

32
00:03:14,733 --> 00:03:16,033
I'll wait for you until 11 p.m.

33
00:03:54,936 --> 00:03:59,370
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

34
00:04:01,333 --> 00:04:02,366
Why did it take so long?

35
00:04:03,100 --> 00:04:06,100
What do you want
with me at this late hour, Miss Jin?

36
00:04:08,933 --> 00:04:10,000
Why didn't you drive?

37
00:04:12,966 --> 00:04:14,700
I forgot. Actually,

38
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:20,233
I couldn't find the key
when I left, so...

39
00:04:23,214 --> 00:04:27,178
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

40
00:04:27,178 --> 00:04:31,136
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

41
00:04:31,136 --> 00:04:33,024
♪Open my secret♪

42
00:04:33,024 --> 00:04:38,624
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

43
00:04:38,624 --> 00:04:42,432
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

44
00:04:42,432 --> 00:04:47,229
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

45
00:04:47,229 --> 00:04:54,541
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪

46
00:05:12,206 --> 00:05:17,984
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

47
00:05:17,984 --> 00:05:24,647
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

48
00:05:27,933 --> 00:05:31,400
The plan for the new product
has been issued. Remember to read it.

49
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,300
Alright, Mr. Lan.

50
00:05:32,633 --> 00:05:37,200
But for this design,
do we still involve Gu Qianqian's team?

51
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:42,000
If so, their family
would officially enter this field.

52
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:45,333
No need. Come in.

53
00:05:52,433 --> 00:05:54,400
Aren't they Gu Qianqian's assistants?

54
00:05:55,366 --> 00:05:58,433
Yes, I put them on her team.

55
00:06:00,166 --> 00:06:02,933
They have fully mastered
all the technologies.

56
00:06:02,966 --> 00:06:04,333
And following your thoughts,

57
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:07,500
I acquired not only a company
engaging in the campus field,

58
00:06:07,833 --> 00:06:09,966
but also a tech team
of university students.

59
00:06:10,733 --> 00:06:13,933
They will lead and develop
the Gemini products.

60
00:06:16,333 --> 00:06:20,900
We'll be the decision-makers again,
and the cost is controllable.

61
00:06:25,433 --> 00:06:26,533
I have never given up.

62
00:06:27,500 --> 00:06:30,333
I've always been contemplating,
designing

63
00:06:31,533 --> 00:06:33,166
and shouldering my responsibilities,

64
00:06:34,133 --> 00:06:35,733
and I've found my passion.

65
00:06:38,233 --> 00:06:40,400
What do you think is the soul
of the product?

66
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:45,333
It means the inner essence.

67
00:06:45,333 --> 00:06:46,733
How can a product last without love?

68
00:06:48,133 --> 00:06:50,233
Not just market data.

69
00:06:50,966 --> 00:06:52,100
Because only with passion,

70
00:06:52,700 --> 00:06:53,566
can it have a soul

71
00:06:54,833 --> 00:06:55,966
and stand the test of time.

72
00:07:02,366 --> 00:07:04,233
(Beauty Bulletin)
(After a brief sales slump,)

73
00:07:04,433 --> 00:07:07,533
(WE Group has launched its new product
Plus in the Gemini Twins series,)

74
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,966
(which is infused
with love, soul and passion,)

75
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:13,433
(breaking the bottleneck
and creating another sales legend.)

76
00:07:14,016 --> 00:07:18,880
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

77
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:24,589
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

78
00:07:24,589 --> 00:07:31,070
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

79
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:36,787
♪Anything I say can't fully describe♪

80
00:07:36,787 --> 00:07:42,208
♪My feelings for you♪

81
00:07:42,208 --> 00:07:44,768
♪Please give me more time♪

82
00:07:44,768 --> 00:07:48,608
♪Let me stay longer♪

83
00:07:48,608 --> 00:07:53,184
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

84
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:58,170
(Market Research Report)
For the lipstick, I want you guys

85
00:07:58,170 --> 00:08:00,033
to focus on its packaging,

86
00:08:00,033 --> 00:08:03,766
because many women don't buy it
for the lipstick's shade.

87
00:08:03,766 --> 00:08:05,400
Can everyone write a plan?

88
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,133
Let's end the meeting
for today. Thank you.

89
00:08:07,133 --> 00:08:10,875
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

90
00:08:13,366 --> 00:08:14,624
Like this. Look.

91
00:08:16,033 --> 00:08:17,300
One.

92
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:18,848
One.

93
00:08:19,033 --> 00:08:19,966
Throw a punch.

94
00:08:19,966 --> 00:08:20,966
One.

95
00:08:20,966 --> 00:08:21,952
Two.

96
00:08:22,733 --> 00:08:23,800
Two.

97
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,900
You're doing this hand wrong.

98
00:08:32,566 --> 00:08:34,433
Look fierce.

99
00:08:45,233 --> 00:08:46,100
Congratulations, Mr. Lan.

100
00:08:47,300 --> 00:08:49,700
You have now been among the top two
of our investment list.

101
00:08:50,166 --> 00:08:51,500
Looking forward to your bid.

102
00:08:52,166 --> 00:08:53,833
How many companies
will you invest in this year?

103
00:08:55,300 --> 00:08:57,504
One.

104
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,166
Then the other one is...

105
00:09:03,966 --> 00:09:05,333
It's the Gu family's new company.

106
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,366
Do you also invest in new companies?

107
00:09:10,300 --> 00:09:11,933
Yeah. Mr. Lan, don't misunderstand.

108
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,033
It's not because I'm related to them.

109
00:09:15,633 --> 00:09:17,133
(Financing Plan )
Although that's a new company,

110
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,166
its ranking is rising rapidly.

111
00:09:19,533 --> 00:09:21,233
Every new product
they have launched is popular,

112
00:09:21,533 --> 00:09:24,300
and they have quickly occupied
most of the lower-tier market.

113
00:09:25,500 --> 00:09:27,433
They're using
the beachhead-and-advance strategy.

114
00:09:28,433 --> 00:09:30,333
You have to be careful.

115
00:09:43,366 --> 00:09:46,300
Lan Chen, I have something
to discuss with you.

116
00:09:50,566 --> 00:09:51,733
Any problems?

117
00:09:54,433 --> 00:09:56,833
No. I was thinking about
the Gu family's new beauty company.

118
00:09:59,233 --> 00:10:00,800
There's something I'd like to discuss.

119
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:03,333
What's it?

120
00:10:03,333 --> 00:10:08,233
I accepted a job offer
to be a fighting coach overseas.

121
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:13,000
How long are you going to be gone?

122
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:14,566
A season takes half a year.

123
00:10:15,233 --> 00:10:16,733
Then I can rest for three months.

124
00:10:19,433 --> 00:10:21,100
But it's quite good to stay here.

125
00:10:21,133 --> 00:10:23,400
And what am I going to do
without you here?

126
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:24,900
I think a good relationship

127
00:10:25,133 --> 00:10:27,700
must be about supporting
each other to become better.

128
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,433
Then when are you leaving?

129
00:10:34,333 --> 00:10:37,366
I'll fly in three days.

130
00:10:39,133 --> 00:10:40,433
It's okay.

131
00:10:40,433 --> 00:10:44,600
I hope you're a good fashion designer
when I come back.

132
00:10:48,333 --> 00:10:52,533
Okay, just in case you forget me
when you're out there,

133
00:10:53,433 --> 00:10:55,133
we should get
our marriage certificate first.

134
00:10:57,833 --> 00:11:00,300
Who wants to marry you?
I'm still young.

135
00:11:00,966 --> 00:11:03,533
Why do I have to tie myself down to you?

136
00:11:03,633 --> 00:11:06,966
But you've already tied
yourself down to me tightly.

137
00:11:13,100 --> 00:11:14,200
Let's take a look over there.

138
00:11:14,766 --> 00:11:16,032
Let's go.

139
00:11:23,766 --> 00:11:25,300
Why is it a bridal shop?

140
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:33,533
Welcome. What a perfect match. Come in.

141
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:36,400
Don't stand there. Come on in.

142
00:11:36,933 --> 00:11:40,000
Move. There are many beautiful dresses
for your choice.

143
00:12:39,206 --> 00:12:43,728
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

144
00:12:46,758 --> 00:12:51,719
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

145
00:12:54,768 --> 00:13:00,592
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

146
00:13:00,592 --> 00:13:08,062
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

147
00:13:08,062 --> 00:13:11,543
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

148
00:13:11,543 --> 00:13:15,664
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

149
00:13:15,664 --> 00:13:17,360
♪Open my secret♪

150
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:23,408
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

151
00:13:23,408 --> 00:13:27,280
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

152
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:31,786
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

153
00:13:31,786 --> 00:13:40,496
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
